The Alex Jones Show 
Sunday, 17 November 2013


[sebaygo1]

Show description from theweb site :: On this live Sunday, November 17 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex covers the historic collapse of an American presidency as Obama continues to flounder and flail in the intense backlash over Obamacare. The president's proposal to allow insurance companies to keep offering healthcare plans cancelled by Obamacare will likely increase premium rates even more. 

Oprah Winfrey once again plays the race card by suggesting that anyone critical of the government healthcare takeover is "racist." 

Sen. Ted Cruz cuts through this spin by pointing out that Obamacare is the best example of the enormous rift between Washington and We the People.
